OL,7,FAmong the most drastic changes that
OL,8,Fresidents will feel is a 9.99%
OL,9,Fincrease to council tax for the next
OL,10,Ftwo years, meaning that by 2026
OL,11,Fcouncil tax would increase by 21%.
OL,13,FThis means that if you're on the
OL,14,Flowest rate of council tax in
OL,15,FBirmingham, you'd be paying #1524.58,
OL,16,Fup from #1270.48.
OL,18,FBirmingham City Council has also
OL,19,Frequested a #1.25 billion bailout to
OL,20,Fthe Government, to help balance the
OL,21,Fbooks.
